<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ellie3" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3656445); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3656445&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608430610" alt="Ellie3" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3656445)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ellie3" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3656445); return false;">Ellie3</a></span> , author of <a href="/the-apple-doesn-t-fall-far">The Apple Doesn't Fall Far</a>.</li>
